{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"127971-juvia-juvia-traey-la-aalegria","title":"¡Lluvia lluvia trae la alegría!","description":"¡Roda junto con la nube y siente la felicidad que trae!","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Aboli Chowdhary"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/127971-juvia-juvia-traey-la-aalegria"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/790870/size3/6cce451176ed21d91d7cbf567d30f1c0.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/790870/size6/6cce451176ed21d91d7cbf567d30f1c0.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8743/size6/4a76145e7beb91fff2c10f65f9baa71b.jpg","text":"Una nube rodaba alegremente en el cielo.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8744/size6/3135a8e1073c74bce26f50245c4216d2.jpg","text":"El pavo real dijo, \"¿Por qué no llueves? Voy a bailar por ti.\"","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8745/size6/63ff43e947322a615f08887759ffc037.jpg","text":"El pez dijo, \"Llueva por favor, necesito más agua\".","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8746/size6/5bdb3d47b093b96939a9a5ad7c2fd45b.jpg","text":"El granjero dijo, \"Por favor llueva. Plantaré semillas para la próxima cosecha.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8747/size6/3f0a57199dec0237eef8309980514262.jpg","text":"Raju dijo, \"Si llueve, navegaré los barcos de papel\".","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8748/size6/8fd45f41b465249650ca93bf92d04c6a.jpg","text":"Y entonces, empezó a llover.\nLa lluvia parecía las gotas relucientes de perlas.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8749/size6/4565dba217f4aed7be9cb51fd123460c.jpg","text":"El pavo real extendió sus bonitas plumas y bailó.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8750/size6/f4bee299690e8353c4636bfe107bd05a.jpg","text":"El estanque se llenó. El pez estaba feliz.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8751/size6/c9c57b020cec0f1b07044edb59ccefd2.jpg","text":"El granjero empezó a plantar semillas.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8752/size6/13eefcbc569c958f5ae5453232cb7bb0.jpg","text":"¡Chof! ¡Plas! ¡Plas! Raju y sus amigos lo pasaron muy bien en los charcos.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/8753/size6/fb21885f9ec50b5c040c56623e7cb82b.jpg","text":"La nube llenó el corazón de todos de alegría. Siguió adelante. Todos los niños se despidieron.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":116}}